outputs.name: Message
outputs.value:
As you draw near the entrance to the old forest, a subtle shift in the surroundings becomes apparent.

The air takes on a refreshing crispness, carrying the earthy perfume of moss and foliage. Tall grasses sway gently at the forest's edge, seemingly whispering tales of the mysteries concealed within.

At the threshold, the towering trees stand as sentinels, their trunks adorned with lichens and vines. Sunlight filters through the foliage, casting enchanting patterns on the ground. You catch glimpses of vibrant flowers and small woodland creatures moving in rhythmic choreography.
